Version 0.0.1 - Released 2010-07-16
- Initial Release

Version 0.0.2 - Released 2010-10-25
- Fixed : Used single field in collection instead of dropping and re-adding the collection each time. This was to counteract a problem with MongoDB crashing after many drop and re-adds.

Version 0.0.3 - Release 2011-01-10
- Updated to work with Replica Sets. Added the new class FriskConnection which extends pymongo Connection with our check_health() method
